# constant factor rule: For any constant &quot;c&quot;, formula_14
# product rule (or Leibniz&#x27;s rule): formula_15
# chain rule: If &quot;g&quot; is differentiable at p and &quot;h&quot; is differentiable at &quot;g&quot;(p), then formula_16

