===The Lie derivative===
The Lie derivative of a vector field formula_21 along a vector field formula_22 is given by the difference of two directional derivatives (with vanishing torsion):
formula_23
In particular, for a scalar field formula_24, the Lie derivative reduces to the standard directional derivative:
